https://www.reddit.com/r/dailyprogrammer/comments/vsv3v/6292012_challenge_70_intermediate/

Implement the hyperoperator as a function hyper(n, a, b), for non-negative
integers n, a, b.

hyper(1, a, b) = a + b, hyper(2, a, b) = a * b, hyper(3, a, b) = a ^ b, etc.

Bonus points for efficient implementations.

thanks to noodl for the challenge at /r/dailyprogrammer_ideas ! ..
If you think yo have a challenge worthy for our sub, do not hesitate to submit it there!
